<li>Horzepa, Stan, "<i><a href="http://www.arrl.org/news/features/2003/10/10/1/" class="external text" title="http://www.arrl.org/news/features/2003/10/10/1/" rel="nofollow">Surfin': Who Invented Radio</a>?</i>" Arrl.org. 10 October 2003.</li>
